{"tid":326451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡小姐16強被網民批質素低    主辦機構：心地善良也重要","createTime":"2017-07-18T04:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T11:02:07.000Z","uid":79563,"like":48,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0087e16b7c859151a2b75597d7b7a86ce609a859","tid":326451,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://l.yimg.com/os/creatr-images/GLB/2017-07-16/49cded40-6a80-11e7-ac1d-27cd17d7b278_15000195822577Yfbkqa3rdk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fl.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-images%2FGLB%2F2017-07-16%2F49cded40-6a80-11e7-ac1d-27cd17d7b278_15000195822577Yfbkqa3rdk.jpg&h=ceff91d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】「新加坡小姐選美賽」16強入圍佳麗的照片近日曝光，但就被網民狠批樣貌質素低落，甚至直指「驚嚇」、「國際笑話」，負評如潮。然而主辦方就強調美貌不是一切，心地善良也很重要，會評估佳麗對社會的貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n受訪參賽佳麗坦言「我們很受傷害」，但反而會更堅強。22歲佳麗林珍玉是理工生，她受訪時說，網友的批評確實讓她感到傷心，但她從中知道哪里可改進，畢竟參賽原本就是為了改進自己。26歲佳麗施凱玲是行銷人員，她身高1.54米，體重只有38公斤，因身材瘦小，被網民揶揄像是未成年。她受訪時透露，舅舅今年因癌症過世，讓她意識到人生不要留遺憾，所以決定在「超齡」之前參賽。她說：「雖然第一天看到那些負評是很受傷，但我現在反而更有自信。」<br />\n<br />\n選美賽主辦方ERM Group表示，「新加坡小姐選美賽」已辦了29年，宗旨之一就是打破刻板印象，證明每個人都可以變漂亮。他們並在facebook留言「世界上沒有醜女人，只有懶女人。」他們並相信「重新打造」的重要性，會努力訓練佳麗和重新包裝，並強調美貌不是一切，心地善良也很重要，會評估佳麗對社會的貢獻。曾代表新加坡參加亞洲比堅尼小姐及世際小姐比賽的威克斯（Melissa Wix），在facebook貼出自己素顏和選美得獎時化好妝的對比圖片，指出新加坡小姐參賽者並不「醜」，只是需要適當地化妝修飾，而主辦單位有責任提供資源和教導參賽者。她呼籲大眾不要再批評參賽者，批評前應該先照鏡看看自己素顏的樣子。"},{"pid":"20e0aeefe07fa7ce547c8e01d48f4363395aaa7b","tid":326451,"uid":52215,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:19:48.000Z","msg":"嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4417e312c6b8d143f4a2308d3f480d67ce5ebfbb","tid":326451,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:20:08.000Z","msg":"新加坡本身就無乜標準靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc98ff93c89bb47839113f539c5f10c8430df86c","tid":326451,"uid":56620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:21:36.000Z","msg":"咁多排骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e110e900a7467064b314bed7574937d7d67238b","tid":326451,"uid":79563,"like":32,"dislike":3,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:23:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新加坡本身就無乜標準靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.freezewall.com/view/1/BC260/002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.freezewall.com%2Fview%2F1%2FBC260%2F002.jpg&h=3a7144d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88cde6fbf62672bacfb228aa814e718ebf0a674e","tid":326451,"uid":129111,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:23:59.000Z","msg":"平心而論，係評審衰姐，班參選人冇錯嘅"},{"pid":"be85235b8bfcc9237f389697080ac2690ca28e1d","tid":326451,"uid":42879,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:25:07.000Z","msg":"下面右邊數過黎第三個ok呀，唔知有冇睇錯或者比旁邊影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c19d59be3011c07be82ba95dac8124050329c64","tid":326451,"uid":5253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:29:17.000Z","msg":"豬扒大賽？"},{"pid":"337d06f8225c9f0d3f83c07a4579ffcb474877ac","tid":326451,"uid":52942,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:29:47.000Z","msg":"最右個條女比佢入圍即係明做佢姐"},{"pid":"27705eff86c9cf35bbd929031c24099f8e4a04f4","tid":326451,"uid":73262,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:30:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/sw5z6tpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsw5z6tpg&h=daa650ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d967336b95c390a2176c50db7b0bbff2091c1f62","tid":326451,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:30:38.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/