:0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:15:01.000Z","msg":"選美比賽唔睇樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁選完有乜用"},{"pid":"ef4c19ee96c865b99911bd6d018ebc267b1032cd","tid":326451,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:16:16.000Z","msg":"郭妃麗"},{"pid":"d2ee6c9be772d4604f0d17f2b94334bb141d119a","tid":326451,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:16:18.000Z","msg":"得前排右3正常妙少"},{"pid":"bafe652001a3580867396637fa338ae675f2a9f3","tid":326451,"uid":9171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:17:35.000Z","msg":"前排左二<br />\n後排右一<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17ae136ff993342cdd814e259d51c2d634e5986","tid":326451,"uid":44593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:29:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/miss-singapore-beauty-pageant-2017-finalists-photo-draws-flak-online?utm_campaign=Echobox&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=Facebook&amp;xtor=CS1-10#link_time=1499905181\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.straitstimes.com%2Fsingapore%2Fmiss-singapore-beauty-pageant-2017-finalists-photo-draws-flak-online%3Futm_campaign%3DEchobox%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3DFacebook%26xtor%3DCS1-10%23link_time%3D1499905181&d=%2F8JwxMpE5qC8u%2FkABUisAf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=6e2e60b3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/miss-singapore-beauty-pageant-2017-finalists-photo-draws-flak-online?utm_campaign=Echobox&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=Facebook&amp;xtor=CS1-10#link_time=1499905181</a><br />\n<br />\n(入面張圖大少少)<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Of the Singaporeans, one was born in Myanmar and another two were born in China, said the spokesman.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Many netizens also questioned the legitimacy of the event, but the organiser said the pageant has been running for 29 years ...&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Unlike this pageant, the Miss Universe Singapore and Miss Tourism Global Singapore pageants are open only to citizens.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;The Miss Singapore Beauty Pageant had about 60 applications and finalists were <span style=\"color: red;\">chosen by a committee of former pageant winners.</span>&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;Contestants from other pageants have faced harsh criticism too.&quot;</span>"},{"pid":"e7369ed83e0dfda49813925de846be1960f1b9da","tid":326451,"uid":55192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:30:55.000Z","msg":"然而主辦方就強調美貌不是一切，心地善良也很重要，會評估佳麗對社會的貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n其實不否認係咪等同承認？<br />\n<br />\n其實大家近年點睇選美？<br />\n我覺得而家香港「港姐」光環冇幾十年前咁大<br />\n真係靚女都好少真係參選<br />\n反而好似好多去咗外國讀書嘅女女<br />\n可能受上一代影響 先會返香港參選"},{"pid":"f98932f41abbc7da920c28a9a2bc92f87e4214dc","tid":326451,"uid":45591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:32:24.000Z","msg":"你覺得只係見過幾面就介定到佢係心地善良咩<br />\n<br />\n未見過女人定太睇小女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be69663cb1444b711045f66dbae911eb61b5792e","tid":326451,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:33:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你覺得只係見過幾面就介定到佢係心地善良咩<br />\n<br />\n未見過女人定太睇小女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nG來"},{"pid":"8fed1d04b5fd563593337c6a3641a2f458d3b33a","tid":326451,"uid":55192,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:33:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/miss-singapore-beauty-pageant-2017-finalists-photo-draws-flak-online?utm_campaign=Echobox&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=Facebook&amp;xtor=CS1-10#link_time=1499905181\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.straitstimes.com%2Fsingapore%2Fmiss-singapore-beauty-pageant-2017-finalists-photo-draws-flak-online%3Futm_campaign%3DEchobox%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3DFacebook%26xtor%3DCS1-10%23link_time%3D1499905181&d=%2F8JwxMpE5qC8u%2FkABUisAf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=6e2e60b3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/miss-singapore-beauty-pageant-2017-finalists-photo-draws-flak-online?utm_campaign=Echobox&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=Facebook&amp;xtor=CS1-10#link_time=1499905181</a><br />\n<br />\n(入面張圖大少少)<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Of the Singaporeans, one was born in Myanmar and another two were born in China, said the spokesman.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Many netizens also questioned the legitimacy of the event, but the organiser said the pageant has been running for 29 years ...&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Unlike this pageant, the Miss Universe Singapore and Miss Tourism Global Singapore pageants are open only to citizens.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;The Miss Singapore Beauty Pageant had about 60 applications and finalists were <span style=\"color: red;\">chosen by a committee of former pageant winners.</span>&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;Contestants from other pageants have faced harsh criticism too.&quot;</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諗真啲 其實佢地都難做嘅<br />\n你點諗到 「嘩 你都嚟選？」<br />\n奈何大部份係豬扒時 佢只能夠揀最好嘅十幾個出嚟<br />\n<br />\n退一步諗 喂其實可能呢度呢啲已經係當中最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aea72686eb6231d8498a85df17d0d9579f2178b","tid":326451,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:37:10.000Z","msg":"右上角選美都戴眼鏡....咩玩法?"},{"pid":"085bf75030c8456e923e171f63c737b20dd811e3","tid":326451,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:39:36.000Z","msg":"下左二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8645